content: I am trying to apply changes of https://jira.hl7.org/browse/FHIR-27914 which update the extension ElementDefinition.minvalue http://hl7.org/fhir/extension-minvalue.html. I want double check before I start: I need to update this file: source\profile\element-extensions-spreadsheet.xml. Should I open it as xml or as excel? Is there anything else I need to do after update this file? @Lloyd McKenzie
Definitely Excel. I don't think you'll need to do anything else
